// /set-up — single Vibe Code block, the whole post-payment onboarding setup.
// Six sub-steps in one chat with Lee:
//   1. Set up your brand                (lifted from screen-2)
//   2. Choose your review mode          (lifted from screen-4)
//   3. How Brieflee works  · skippable  (lifted from screen-5)
//   4. QA Checklist        · skippable  (Bev's copy + qa_checklist multi-select)
//   5. Thresholds          · skippable  (9 single-select threshold fields)
//   6. Review your content blueprint    (lifted from screen-3 blueprint half)
//
// SOFTR CONFIG REQUIRED:
//   Source tab: bind to ACCOUNTS in "brieflee beta", filter to logged-in user.
//   Actions tab: auto-populated from updateFields aliases below.
//
// UX rules:
//   • Each sub-step reveals as a chat sequence (typing → bubble → card).
//   • Once a sub-step saves or skips, its big input card collapses to a single
//     "✓ Saved" / "↷ Skipped" line and the next sub-step's chat reveals below.
//   • The page smooth-scrolls to the new sub-step so the active conversation
//     stays in view.
//   • Top progress dots (one per sub-step) light up as the user advances —
//     same pattern as screen-3.
//   • After the final blueprint save we redirect to /new.

